@page "/check-in-checkout"

<PageTitle>Check-in y checkout</PageTitle>

<div class="process-page">
    <section class="process-hero">
        <div class="process-hero__content">
            <div class="process-badge process-badge--glass">Guía para huéspedes</div>
            <h1>Proceso de check-in y checkout</h1>
            <p>
                Conoce cómo preparar tu llegada, validar tu reservación, recibir tu habitación y cerrar tu estancia
                de forma ordenada dentro de HotelChain Collection.
            </p>

            <div class="process-hero__actions">
                <a class="process-btn process-btn--light" href="/checkout">Consultar mi reservación</a>
                <a class="process-btn process-btn--ghost" href="/search">Buscar hoteles</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-hero__visual">
            <article class="process-visual-card process-visual-card--checkin">
                <span>01</span>
                <strong>Llegada y validación</strong>
            </article>
            <article class="process-visual-card process-visual-card--room">
                <span>02</span>
                <strong>Asignación de habitación</strong>
            </article>
            <article class="process-visual-card process-visual-card--account">
                <span>03</span>
                <strong>Cuenta y comprobante</strong>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="process-intro-grid">
        <article class="process-intro-card">
            <span class="process-intro-card__label">Antes de llegar</span>
            <strong>Ten a mano tu código de reserva</strong>
            <p>Esto ayuda a recepción a encontrar tu registro y validar más rápido tus datos.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="process-intro-card">
            <span class="process-intro-card__label">Durante la estancia</span>
            <strong>Los consumos se registran en tu cuenta</strong>
            <p>Restaurante, room service u otros cargos pueden acumularse hasta el cierre.</p>
        </article>

        <article class="process-intro-card">
            <span class="process-intro-card__label">Al salir</span>
            <strong>La cuenta debe quedar liquidada</strong>
            <p>Antes del checkout se revisan cargos pendientes y se genera el comprobante final.</p>
        </article>
    </section>

    <section class="process-section">
        <div class="process-section__header">
            <div>
                <div class="process-badge">Llegada</div>
                <h2>¿Cómo funciona el check-in?</h2>
                <p>
                    El check-in confirma tu llegada, valida los datos de la reserva y permite asignar una habitación
                    física disponible para iniciar tu estancia.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-steps process-steps--checkin">
            <article class="process-step process-step--featured">
                <div class="process-step__number">1</div>
                <h3>Presenta tu reservación</h3>
                <p>
                    Ten a mano tu código de reserva y documento de identificación para agilizar el ingreso.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="process-step">
                <div class="process-step__number">2</div>
                <h3>Validación de identidad</h3>
                <p>
                    El personal puede confirmar fechas, huéspedes registrados y condiciones de la reserva.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="process-step">
                <div class="process-step__number">3</div>
                <h3>Asignación de habitación</h3>
                <p>
                    Recepción asigna una habitación física disponible según el tipo de habitación reservado.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="process-step">
                <div class="process-step__number">4</div>
                <h3>Información de estancia</h3>
                <p>
                    Recibe indicaciones sobre horarios, reglas, amenidades y canales de atención del hotel.
                </p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="process-section process-section--split">
        <div class="process-photo-card process-photo-card--reception">
            <div>
                <span>Recepción</span>
                <strong>Ingreso ordenado</strong>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-section__content">
            <div class="process-badge">Durante la estancia</div>
            <h2>Cuenta de estancia y cargos incidentales</h2>
            <p>
                Durante tu hospedaje pueden registrarse cargos por restaurante, room service, minibar u otros servicios.
                Estos cargos se revisan al momento de liquidar la cuenta antes del checkout.
            </p>

            <div class="process-mini-grid">
                <article>
                    <span>Base</span>
                    <strong>Reserva pagada</strong>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <span>Cargos</span>
                    <strong>Consumos de estancia</strong>
                </article>
                <article>
                    <span>Cierre</span>
                    <strong>Liquidación final</strong>
                </article>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="process-section">
        <div class="process-section__header">
            <div>
                <div class="process-badge">Salida</div>
                <h2>¿Cómo funciona el checkout?</h2>
                <p>
                    El checkout cierra formalmente tu hospedaje, revisa los cargos de estancia y deja disponible
                    el comprobante final de la reservación.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-steps process-steps--checkout">
            <article class="process-step process-step--featured">
                <div class="process-step__number">1</div>
                <h3>Confirma tu salida</h3>
                <p>
                    Acércate a recepción o sigue el procedimiento indicado para informar la finalización de tu hospedaje.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="process-step">
                <div class="process-step__number">2</div>
                <h3>Revisión de cuenta</h3>
                <p>
                    El personal valida cargos de restaurante, minibar, room service u otros consumos registrados.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="process-step">
                <div class="process-step__number">3</div>
                <h3>Liquidación final</h3>
                <p>
                    Antes de cerrar la reserva, cualquier saldo pendiente debe quedar liquidado.
                </p>
            </article>

            <article class="process-step">
                <div class="process-step__number">4</div>
                <h3>Comprobante</h3>
                <p>
                    Después del checkout, conserva tu código y descarga el PDF como comprobante final.
                </p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="process-timeline">
        <article class="process-timeline__item">
            <span>Antes de llegar</span>
            <strong>Reserva y documentos</strong>
        </article>
        <article class="process-timeline__item">
            <span>Ingreso</span>
            <strong>Validación y habitación</strong>
        </article>
        <article class="process-timeline__item">
            <span>Estancia</span>
            <strong>Servicios y cargos</strong>
        </article>
        <article class="process-timeline__item">
            <span>Salida</span>
            <strong>Liquidación y PDF</strong>
        </article>
    </section>

    <section class="process-section">
        <div class="process-section__header">
            <div>
                <div class="process-badge">Casos comunes</div>
                <h2>Situaciones que el huésped debería conocer</h2>
                <p>
                    Algunas solicitudes pueden depender de disponibilidad, política del hotel, inventario y reglas comerciales activas.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="process-scenarios-grid">
            <article class="process-scenario-card">
                <h3>Late check-in</h3>
                <p>Si llegarás fuera del horario habitual, notifica al hotel para evitar incidencias operativas o tratamiento de no-show.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="process-scenario-card">
                <h3>Salida tardía</h3>
                <p>Puede estar sujeta a disponibilidad, política del hotel y cargos adicionales.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="process-scenario-card">
                <h3>Cargos incidentales</h3>
                <p>Consumos como restaurante, minibar o room service pueden agregarse a la cuenta de estancia.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="process-scenario-card">
                <h3>Cambio de fechas</h3>
                <p>Disponible según política, inventario, reglas comerciales y anticipación mínima requerida.</p>
            </article>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="process-highlight">
        <div>
            <div class="process-badge">Recomendación</div>
            <h2>Consulta tu reservación antes de llegar</h2>
            <p>
                Revisa fechas, huéspedes registrados, estado de pago y código de reservación. Esto facilita el ingreso,
                evita confusiones y ayuda a que la operación del hotel sea más rápida.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-highlight__actions">
            <a class="process-btn process-btn--dark" href="/checkout">Consultar mi reservación</a>
            <a class="process-btn process-btn--outline" href="/hotel-rules">Ver reglas del hotel</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<style>
    .process-page {
        color: #111827;
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .process-hero {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 460px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.05fr) minmax(360px, 0.95fr);
        gap: 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 32px;
        overflow: hidden;
        padding: 1.25rem;
        background:
            linear-gradient(110deg, rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.86), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.58), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18)),
            url('https://res.cloudinary.com/ds7fyjtcc/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,c_fill,g_auto,w_1800,h_1000/v1777220508/AmenitiesMostrador_qflglt.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
    }

    .process-hero__content {
        color: #fff;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: flex-end;
        padding: 1.6rem;
        max-width: 780px;
    }

    .process-hero h1,
    .process-section h2,
    .process-highlight h2 {
        margin: 0;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        color: #0f172a;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .process-hero h1 {
        color: #fff;
        font-size: clamp(2.45rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
        line-height: 0.98;
        max-width: 720px;
    }

    .process-hero p {
        margin: 1rem 0 0;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        line-height: 1.75;
        max-width: 760px;
    }

    .process-hero__actions,
    .process-highlight__actions {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        margin-top: 1.4rem;
    }

    .process-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 46px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 0.78rem 1.1rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 900;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
    }

    .process-btn--light {
        background: #fff;
        color: #0f172a;
    }

    .process-btn--ghost {
        color: #fff;
        border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
        backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    }

    .process-btn--dark {
        background: #0f172a;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .process-btn--outline {
        background: #fff;
        color: #0f172a;
        border-color: #cbd5e1;
    }

    .process-btn:hover {
        opacity: 0.95;
    }

    .process-badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        width: max-content;
        padding: 0.38rem 0.78rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #eef2ff;
        color: #1e3a8a;
        font-size: 0.76rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    .process-badge--glass {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.16);
        color: #fff;
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }

    .process-hero__visual {
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.9rem;
        align-content: end;
    }

    .process-visual-card {
        min-height: 132px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 24px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.28);
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18);
    }

    .process-visual-card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15,23,42,0.08), rgba(15,23,42,0.64));
    }

    .process-visual-card span,
    .process-visual-card strong {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .process-visual-card span {
        display: inline-flex;
        margin: 1rem 1rem 0;
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 0.28rem 0.58rem;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
        font-size: 0.74rem;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .process-visual-card strong {
        position: absolute;
        left: 1rem;
        bottom: 1rem;
        right: 1rem;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .process-visual-card--checkin {
        background-image: url('https://res.cloudinary.com/ds7fyjtcc/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,c_fill,g_auto,w_900,h_420/v1777220508/AmenitiesMostrador_qflglt.jpg');
    }

    .process-visual-card--room {
        background-image: url('https://res.cloudinary.com/ds7fyjtcc/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,c_fill,g_auto,w_900,h_420/v1777220507/AmenitiesLobby_s5mpwo.jpg');
    }

    .process-visual-card--account {
        background-image: url('https://res.cloudinary.com/ds7fyjtcc/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,c_fill,g_auto,w_900,h_420/v1777220512/AmenitiesServicioMesa_lje42y.jpg');
    }

    .process-intro-grid,
    .process-scenarios-grid,
    .process-timeline,
    .process-mini-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .process-intro-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .process-intro-card,
    .process-step,
    .process-scenario-card,
    .process-timeline__item,
    .process-highlight,
    .process-section--split {
        background: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.07);
    }

    .process-intro-card {
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .process-intro-card__label,
    .process-timeline__item span,
    .process-mini-grid span {
        display: block;
        color: #64748b;
        font-size: 0.74rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }

    .process-intro-card strong,
    .process-timeline__item strong,
    .process-mini-grid strong {
        color: #0f172a;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .process-intro-card p {
        color: #475569;
        margin: 0.55rem 0 0;
        line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .process-section {
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
    }

    .process-section__header {
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .process-section h2,
    .process-highlight h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
    }

    .process-section__header p,
    .process-section__content p,
    .process-highlight p {
        margin: 0.65rem 0 0;
        color: #475569;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 880px;
    }

    .process-steps {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .process-step {
        border-radius: 26px;
        padding: 1.2rem;
        min-height: 230px;
    }

    .process-step--featured {
        grid-column: span 2;
    }

    .process-step__number {
        width: 42px;
        height: 42px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: #eef2ff;
        color: #1d4ed8;
        font-weight: 900;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .process-step h3,
    .process-scenario-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 0.45rem;
        color: #0f172a;
        font-weight: 900;
        line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .process-step p,
    .process-scenario-card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #475569;
        line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .process-section--split {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(300px, 0.8fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
        gap: 1rem;
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 1rem;
        align-items: stretch;
    }

    .process-photo-card {
        min-height: 330px;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border-radius: 24px;
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-end;
        padding: 1.2rem;
    }

    .process-photo-card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15,23,42,0.05), rgba(15,23,42,0.58));
    }

    .process-photo-card > div {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .process-photo-card span {
        display: inline-flex;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
        padding: 0.25rem 0.58rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
    }

    .process-photo-card strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.45rem;
        font-weight: 900;
    }

    .process-photo-card--reception {
        background-image: url('https://res.cloudinary.com/ds7fyjtcc/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto,c_fill,g_auto,w_1000,h_900/v1777220511/AmenitiesSalaEspera_mymp92.jpg');
    }

    .process-section__content {
        padding: 1rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .process-mini-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        margin-top: 1.1rem;
    }

    .process-mini-grid article {
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: #f8fafc;
        padding: 0.95rem;
    }

    .process-timeline {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .process-timeline__item {
        border-radius: 22px;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .process-scenarios-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .process-scenario-card {
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 1rem;
    }

    .process-highlight {
        border-radius: 30px;
        padding: 1.35rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) auto;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: center;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8fbff 100%);
        border-color: #dbeafe;
    }

    .process-highlight__actions {
        justify-content: flex-end;
        margin-top: 0;
    }

    @@media (max-width: 1100px) {
        .process-hero,
        .process-section--split,
        .process-highlight {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .process-hero__visual {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
        }

        .process-steps,
        .process-scenarios-grid,
        .process-timeline {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        }

        .process-highlight__actions {
            justify-content: flex-start;
        }
    }

    @@media (max-width: 760px) {
        .process-hero {
            min-height: auto;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 24px;
        }

        .process-hero__content {
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        .process-hero__visual,
        .process-intro-grid,
        .process-steps,
        .process-scenarios-grid,
        .process-timeline,
        .process-mini-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }

        .process-step--featured {
            grid-column: auto;
        }
    }
</style>
